        "app_name": "OnePlayer - HD Video Player",
        "app_id": "oneplayer.local.web.video.player.downloader.vault",
        "category": "Video Players & Editors",
        "description": "OnePlayer is a powerful <b>local media app</b> that supports both video and music playback, delivering stunning 4K/Ultra HD video quality and high-fidelity offline music for an exceptional entertainment experience. It allows you to watch your local videos seamlessly. The app also features a private video vault with a secure lock to protect your personal films. Additionally, the music player lets you create custom playlists and enjoy a smooth listening experience.\r\n\r\n💡 <b>Features</b> 💡\r\n- Supports casting local videos to TV\r\n- Supports offline music & video playback\r\n- Automatically scans all local audio and video files\r\n- View by artists, albums, folders, and playlists\r\n- Floating window for multitasking\r\n- Private Video Vault to protect your privacy\r\n- Powerful built-in player to play your local media files\r\n- Easy to control volume, brightness, and playing progress\r\n- Multi-playback options: auto-rotation, aspect-ratio, screen-lock, etc.\r\n- Supports ALL video formats, including MKV, MP4, M4V, AVI, MOV, 3GP, FLV, WMV, RMVB, TS, etc.\r\n- Supports all music and audio formats, like MP3, MIDI, WAV, FLAC, AAC, APE, etc.\r\n\r\n<b>OnePlayer Top Features</b>\r\n🎦 <b>Full-featured Video Player</b>\r\nOnePlayer supports fast and stable offline playback of all video formats. Enjoy smooth playback of all HD, UHD, 4K, and 1080P videos stored on your device. Easily adjust volume, brightness, or progress with a simple swipe. It supports auto-rotation, aspect ratio adjustments, and screen lock.\r\n\r\n🎵 <b>Premium Music Player</b>\r\nOur music player offers high-quality offline playback with shuffle, order, and loop modes. It automatically scans and organizes your local audio files for effortless management. Easily browse by songs, artists, albums, folders, or playlists. Mark favorites, create custom playlists, and set a sleep timer to automatically stop playback—perfect for falling asleep to your favorite tunes.\r\n\r\n💬 <b>Floating Video Player</b>\r\nBoost your productivity with our floating video player! Watch your local videos while using other apps. Move and resize the player effortlessly. Enjoy split-screen multitasking like never before.\r\n\r\n✨ <b>Screen-casting Video Player</b>\r\nCast your videos to a larger screen effortlessly. Enjoy your favorite local content on the big screen with ease.\r\n\r\n🔐 <b>Private Video Vault</b>\r\nAdd a PIN or password lock to your private videos, ensuring that only you can view them. You can easily organize and categorize your sensitive personal videos in this highly secure space.\r\n\r\nℹ️ <b>Disclaimer:</b>\r\nOnePlayer is strictly a <b>local video/audio player and media manager</b>. It is designed solely to play media files that users have legally acquired and stored on their own devices. <b>OnePlayer does NOT contain any video or audio downloading features, nor does it support the unauthorized distribution of copyrighted materials.</b>\r\n\r\nDiscover the perfect media companion! OnePlayer offers seamless local video and music playback, supporting all formats for an enhanced entertainment experience.",
