        "category": "Food & Drink",
        "description": "Get food delivery and grocery orders delivered directly to your door in as fast as 30 minutes with our app that helps with your shopping. Let Instacart connect you to your favorite fast food spots, local grocery store or chain and quickly get your favorite eats delivered. Browse, shop, and eat with convenient grocery delivery in just a few taps! Plus, enjoy $0 delivery fee on your first three grocery orders within 14 days of the first order. Service fees, exclusions and terms apply!\r\n\r\nEnjoy getting safe, contactless food delivery, including all of your grocery needs like your favorite healthy food, snack eats, home essentials, and drinks. Shop your grocery list, explore products from grocery stores around you, and get them delivered to your doorstep. Our grocery technology shopping app helps you save money and time by avoiding multiple trips to the grocery store.\r\n\r\nWith Instacart, grocery savings are made easy. Shop the best of grocery and food technology services all in one easy-to-use shopping app. Order snack eats, food from fresh food markets, drinks, and other household items online and shop with same-day delivery across the US. Prefer pick up? Make your grocery orders online, pick up at your local store, and skip the delivery fee. Download the app to see what supermarkets are available in your zip code for online shopping.\r\n\r\nJust imagine what you can do with on-demand grocery store delivery through Instacart! From getting deliveries in as fast as 30-minutes to grocery coupons to help you save – Instacart has it all. Download your new favorite grocery store shopping app today!\r\n\r\nShopping for fresh food and groceries on Instacart is easy:\r\n\r\n1. Enter your zip code before shopping for your grocery store list\r\n2. Shop online for household items, electronics, ingredients, snacks, and fresh food\r\n3. Get exclusive discounts from local grocery store sales\r\n4. Add your items to your cart and place your order\r\n5. Chat with your shopper in real time to make any changes to your grocery store order\r\n6. Get your shopping delivered straight to your door or skip the delivery fee and pick up at the store\r\n\r\nINSTACART FEATURES\r\n\r\nGROCERY STORE SAVINGS & EASY SHOPPING\r\n- Shop your entire grocery store list delivered in as fast as 30 minutes\r\n- Drinks, fresh food, and snack eats directly delivered straight to you, from grocery stores around you for convenient and fast shopping\r\n- Find grocery savings on drinks and home essentials available while online shopping\r\n- Get quick and safe orders with our contactless delivery shopping app options\r\n\r\nSAVE TIME WITH OUR FRESH FOOD & GROCERY STORE SHOPPING APP\r\n- Skip visiting supermarkets and get more done with your day when you use Instacart to complete your grocery list\r\n- Grocery store savings on fresh produce, beverages, and late-night snacks\r\n- Explore your grocery store from the comfort of your home and shop conveniently - Instacart helps you bring it all so you can do more\r\n\r\nSHOP WITH COUPONS AND DEALS FOR YOUR GROCERY LIST\r\n- Grocery store savings found on some of your favorite products with Instacart\r\n- Discover exclusive deals and grocery coupons found only on the Instacart app\r\n- Shop your grocery store list, store sales, and get better prices on produce, home essentials, snack eats, and drinks\r\n\r\nONLINE SHOPPING FOR GROCERY STORES NEAR YOU\r\n- Instacart connects you with over 85,000 supermarkets and stores across North America\r\n- Shop from your favorite stores – Aldi, Publix, Costco, Safeway and many more\r\n- You can also support local supermarkets. Simply browse and shop with our app!\r\n\r\nInstacart helps bring you fresh products, savory snack eats, cold beverages, and everything you need to complete your grocery store shopping. Get even more perks with Instacart+.\r\n\r\nDownload Instacart today and discover a faster, safer, and more convenient way to shop at grocery stores.\r\n\r\n