    {
        "app_name": "Instamart: Groceries & more",
        "app_id": "in.swiggy.android.instamart",
        "category": "Shopping",
        "description": "With Instamart, get delivery of groceries & more to your doorstep!* Order Vegetables, Kitchen essentials, Electronics, Beauty products, Home decor etc - right to your door. Shop from over 30,000+ products from the best grocery shopping app.\r\n\r\n✅ High-quality groceries, fruits & vegetable delivery \r\n✅ Curd, bread, butter, eggs, cheese, paneer and Amul milk home delivery \r\n✅ Ferrero Rocher & Cadbury chocolates, Pringles chips, Karachi Bakery biscuits\r\n✅ Soft drinks, Bisleri water, snacks, ice, ice cream etc via Instamart\r\n✅ Atta, rice, pulses, cooking oil, spices, noodles etc & more on the groceries delivery app\r\n✅ Personal care products, detergents, cleaning supplies\r\n✅ Baby care, diapers, baby food essentials\r\n✅ Pet food, pet necessities & more\r\n✅ Everyday electronics like chargers, bulbs, batteries\r\n✅ Kitchen gadgets like choppers, blenders, grinders \r\n✅ Puja supplies at the best grocery store app\r\n✅ Stationery items for work & school\r\n✅ Cool gadgets like smartwatches, headphones, LED lights\r\n✅ Emergency supplies like torches, first aid, band-aids\r\n\r\n\r\n🥕 Free Delivery on the freshest fruits and vegetables \r\nOrder vegetables online & get tomatoes, avocado, fruits and more with Instamart, the grocery delivery app. \r\n\r\n\r\n💰 Many safe payment options + cash on delivery too!\r\nInstamart, a grocery shopping app delivery for everyday needs. Pay securely for groceries & other products with UPI, Cash on delivery, or cards / wallets / netbanking / LazyPay. We accept Sodexo meal pass too.\r\n\r\n\r\n💸 Low prices groceries delivery, amazing offers 24x7\r\nInstamart Grocery delivery app brings discounts, savings, deals & bank offers on groceries with free delivery. Enjoy the Mega Savings Festival during the first week of every first month– where you get up to 60% off . Also score freebies & discounts on first purchase on Instamart, the best grocery shopping app.\r\n\r\n\r\n🌺 Puja needs & groceries delivery\r\nGet puja essentials like flowers, oil, agarbatti in just a  few clicks. Open our grocery store delivery app to get grocery & enjoy your shopping online. \r\n\r\n\r\n🎊 Festive Essentials in a Flash with Free Delivery\r\nFrom decorations, to balloons, and party supplies for all your events & festivals, like Rakhi, Diwali, Holi, & more. \r\n\r\n\r\n🎁 Perfect gifts\r\nGet free delivery & find a gift for any occasion with Instamart, the best delivery & grocery app. Impress with gifts, whether it's Mother's Day, Father's Day, Valentine's Day, or any special event.\r\n\r\n\r\n🎧 Electronics store with free delivery\r\nWired or bluetooth earphones? Smart watches & LED lights? Shop for electronics via Instamart, finest grocery store delivery app in your city. \r\n\r\n✔️ Now Delivering in 120+ Cities \r\nBengaluru, Chennai, Delhi, Gurgaon, Hyderabad, Kolkata, Mumbai, Noida, Pune, Ahmedabad, Central Goa, Chandigarh, Coimbatore, Dehradun, Faridabad, Indore, Jaipur, Kochi, Lucknow, Mysore, Surat, Thiruvananthapuram, Vadodara, Vijayawada, Vizag, Bhubaneswar, Kozhikode, Nagpur, Nashik, Pondicherry, Mangaluru, Guntur, Bhopal, Thrissur, Varanasi, Rajkot, Ludhiana, Warangal, Kanpur, Udaipur, Amritsar, Salem, Ranchi, Tirupati , Trichy, Manipal, Vellore, Allahabad, Kollam, Khammam, Hubli, Gorakhpur, Belgaum, Sonipat, Kottayam, Agra, Patiala, Kurnool, Ambala, Karimnagar, Panipat, Nellore, Aligarh, Gwalior, Shivamogga, Vapi, Jalandhar, Alappuzha, Sri Ganganagar, Tirupur, Erode, Madurai, Bareilly, Kota, Ujjain, Aurangabad, Roorkee, Kakinada, Mathura, Patna, Meerut, Moradabad, Palakkad, Thoothukudi, Tirunelveli, Raipur, Jamshedpur, Jabalpur, Kanchipuram, Jodhpur, Bathinda, Thanjavur, Siliguri, Thiruvalla, Vizianagaram, Cuttack, Anand, Latur, Nagercoil, Dibrugarh, Rudrapur, Ajmer, Guwahati, Karnal, Tumakuru, Jhansi, Amravati, Kolhapur, Rajahmundry, Rohtak, Bhilai, Kurukshetra, Davanagere, Karaikkudi, Karur, Berhampur, Durgapur, Bikaner, Satara, Ahmednagar , Saharanpur, Nanded, Lonavala, Silchar & Bilaspur.\r\n\r\n*T&C Apply",
