        "description": "India's #1 Quick Commerce App – Everything delivered in minutes\r\n\r\nZepto delivers 2,00,000+ products to your doorstep in just minutes—from fresh groceries to hot meals, electronics to fashion.\r\n\r\nWhy Zepto Beats Everyone Else\r\n💰 Everyday Lowest Prices\r\nSame products, better prices. No markup games. Get groceries, atta, dal, milk, bread & daily essentials cheaper than anywhere else.\r\n\r\n🚫 Zero Fees\r\nWhat you see is what you pay. No delivery fees (orders ₹99+), no handling fees, no surge fees, no rain charges. Ever.\r\n\r\n⚡ Quick Delivery within minutes, Every Time\r\nOrder now, get it now. Live track your order from our dark store to your door. No waiting. No delays.\r\n\r\nEverything You Need, Instantly\r\n\r\n🍎Fresh Fruits & Vegetables: Hand-picked apples, bananas, tomatoes, leafy greens, exotic fruits\r\n🥛Dairy & Breads: Milk, curd, paneer, butter, bread, cheese\r\n🌾Pantry Staples: Atta, rice, dal, oil, ghee, masalas, sugar, salt, bread\r\n🍪Snacks & Beverages: Biscuits, namkeen, chips, cold drinks, tea, coffee, chocolates, sauces, cereals, Maggi noodles, mixers\r\n🧴Personal Care: Shampoo, soap, face wash, toothpaste, skincare\r\n🧹Household Essentials: Detergent, dishwash, cleaning supplies, toilet paper\r\n👶Baby Care: Diapers, wipes, baby food, baby care products\r\n🐾Pet Supplies: Dog food, cat food, pet treats & accessories\r\n🍗Meat & Eggs: Fresh meat, chicken, fish, seafood, poultry, eggs, frozen meat\r\n\r\nZepto SUPERMALL goes beyond groceries to all your shopping needs. Your one-stop quick commerce destination for:\r\n\r\n📱Electronics: Headphones, smartwatches, chargers, mobile accessories, cables, LED lights\r\n👗Fashion: T-shirts, jeans, activewear, bags, footwear\r\n💄Beauty & Makeup: Lipsticks, makeup, skincare, hair care, fragrances\r\n🏠Home & Kitchen: Cookware, blenders, choppers, home decor, kitchenware\r\n☕Zepto Café: Fresh coffee, tea, hot meals delivered instantly\r\n💍Jewellery & Accessories: Trendy jewellery for every occasion\r\n🏋️Fitness & Wellness: Gym supplements, protein powder, whey powder, fitness gear, gym gear\r\n💊Pharmacy: Medicines, health essentials, vitamins, supplements, tablets, pills, syrup\r\n🧸Toys & Kids: Toys, games, kids' apparel, kids’ stationery, baby food, diaper, story books\r\n🌸Puja Essentials: Incense sticks, flowers, puja items\r\n🎁Gifting: Birthday gifts, anniversary gifts, festive specials, corporate gifting\r\n🐾Pet Food: Dog food, cat food, and treats\r\n\r\nZepto Café: Fresh Food Delivered in Minutes\r\n\r\nOrder hot, fresh meals delivered instantly. Pair your grocery shopping with delicious food delivery. From breakfast to late-night cravings, get restaurant-quality meals in just minutes at your doorstep.\r\nBuy Hot & Cold Beverages, Quick Snacks & Bites, Fresh Meals & Combos, Desserts & Sweets and Healthy Options.\r\n\r\nWhy Millions of Users Choose Zepto?\r\n\r\n🎯Live Order Tracking: Track your order in real-time from store to doorstep\r\n💳Flexible Payments: Cash on Delivery (COD), UPI, cards, wallets, netbanking\r\n🛡️100% Quality Guarantee: Fresh products, every time\r\n🎉Daily Deals & Offers: Exclusive discounts on top brands\r\n💬 24/7 Customer Support: We're always here to help\r\n\r\nShop Your Favorite Brands\r\nAmul, Nestlé, Coca-Cola, Lay's, Britannia, Parle, Ferrero, Nutella, Cadbury, Oreo, Aashirvaad, Fortune, Saffola, Patanjali, ITC, Colgate, Dettol, Surf Excel, Dove, Lakmé, Mamaearth, boAt, Licious, Davidoff, Rage Coffee, Wingreens Farms, Gunsberg, The Baker’s Dozen, Jimmy's Cocktails, Nivea, Haldiram's, Bikano, Heinz, Vahdam, Dettol, Durex, Stayfree, Mymuse, Akshayakalpa, Country Delight, Beco, 24 Mantra, Pepsi, Kurkure, Epigamia, Myprotein & 10,000+ more brands.\r\n\r\nAvailable in 50+ Cities\r\nFast delivery across Bengaluru, Mumbai, Delhi, NCR (Gurugram, Noida, Ghaziabad), Hyderabad, Chennai, Pune, Kolkata, Ahmedabad, Jaipur, Chandigarh, Lucknow, Surat, Kanpur, Kochi, Dehradun, Ludhiana, Nagpur, Meerut & many more.\r\n\r\nDownload Zepto now! Your first delivery within minutes at the lowest price awaits. 🚀\r\n*Terms and Conditions Apply. Visit Zepto Platform Terms of Use for detailed terms",
