        "app_name": "TD Bank (US)",
        "app_id": "com.tdbank",
        "category": "Finance",
        "description": "Bank how you want, when you want. \r\n\r\nPay your bills with ease, deposit checks 24/7, transfer money between your accounts, and more.  \r\n\r\nMORE CONVENIENT EVERYDAY BANKING\r\n\r\nThe TD Bank app makes managing your money easier than ever:\r\n\r\n• View account balances and activity to keep a close eye on where your money is going.\r\n• Curious about your credit score? Check it with just a few taps. \r\n• Pay bills – from one-time, recurring and rush bill payments to getting e-bills, do it all in one place.\r\n• Review account and credit card statements right away.\r\n\r\nCONNECTING YOU WITH FAMILY, FRIENDS & MORE\r\n\r\nWhether you want to send money to friends and family, reduce clutter with paperless statements, or just want to talk, we’ve got you covered:\r\n\r\n• Use Zelle to send money to almost anyone, anywhere in the U.S. using their email or mobile number. It’s quick and easy to set up and get started.\r\n• Add your credit, debit, and ATM cards to your Digital Wallet for easy access to your accounts.\r\n• Sign up for TD for Me Alerts to get personalized messages and never miss a thing.\r\n• Get priority access to customer support when you log in and call through the app – because no one likes waiting on hold.   \r\n\r\nGET PEACE OF MIND\r\n\r\nWith everyday banking at your fingertips, security always comes first. Here’s how we’re committed to making banking more secure for you:\r\n\r\n• The TD Bank app uses industry-standard fingerprint and face recognition for login (on supported devices) and two-step verification (single-use codes) to keep your account secure.\r\n• Lock and unlock credit, debit, and ATM cards instantly – you’re in control.\r\n• Stay on top of your money with customizable TD Alerts that fit your daily banking needs.\r\n\r\n\r\nBy tapping \"Install,\" you consent to the installation of the TD Bank (US) app provided by TD Bank, N.A. and to any future updates/upgrades. You are also acknowledging that you understand that the TD Bank (US) app and any future updates/upgrades will/may perform the functions described below at TD Bank, N.A.'s sole discretion. You may withdraw your consent at any time by deleting or uninstalling this app.\r\n\r\nTD Bank, N.A. Member FDIC",
