        "app_name": "GO2bank: Mobile banking",
        "app_id": "com.greendotcorp.go2bank",
        "category": "Finance",
        "description": "A BETTER WAY TO BANK—GET STARTED TODAY\r\nGO2bank™ makes managing your money easier than ever. Open your account in minutes, grow your savings, and stay covered with overdraft protection, all with the secure mobile banking app designed for your everyday life. \r\n\r\nNO HIDDEN FEES—JUST SMART BANKING\r\nGO2bank puts simple, transparent banking tools at your fingertips so you can skip the monthly fee with eligible direct deposit⁴, avoid hidden fees, and manage your money your way. \r\n\r\nOVERDRAFT PROTECTION FOR LIFE’S CURVEBALLS\r\nGet up to $300 in overdraft protection after eligible direct deposits and opt-in¹. \r\n\r\nGET PAID EARLY—STAY A STEP AHEAD\r\nGet your paycheck up to 2 days early or government benefits, like unemployment, up to 4 days early when you set up direct deposit². Start getting your money on your schedule.\r\n\r\nSAVE SMARTER WITH 4.50% APY\r\nGrow your savings faster with a high-yield savings account that earns 4.50% APY with interest earned quarterly on balances up to $5,000⁶. \r\n\r\nBUILD CREDIT WITH A GO-TO \r\nStart building your credit score, one purchase at a time, one on-time payment at a time, with the GO2bank Secured Visa® Credit Card³.  \r\n\r\nSECURITY & PEACE OF MIND\r\nKeep your money safe with built-in tools you can trust. Lock your card anytime⁸, get real-time fraud alerts⁹, and rest easy knowing your money is FDIC-insured¹⁰.\r\n\r\nNATIONWIDE CASH ACCESS\r\nWithdraw cash for free at thousands of in-network ATMs⁵ or deposit cash at over 90,000 major retailers nationwide⁷. Just use our in-app locator to find locations nearby.\r\n\r\nDownload the GO2bank app today to open an account and start banking with convenience, confidence, and control.\r\n\r\nLEGAL DISCLOSURES\r\nOnline access, mobile number verification (via text message) and identity verification (including SSN) are required to open and use your account.\r\n\r\nMobile number verification, email address verification and mobile app are required to access all features.\r\n\r\n1.\tFees, terms and conditions apply. Learn more at GO2bank.com/overdraft\r\n\r\n2.\tEarly direct deposit availability depends on payor type, timing, payment instructions and bank fraud prevention measures. As such, early direct deposit availability may vary from pay period to pay period.\r\n\r\n3.\tAvailable only to GO2bank accountholders with direct deposits totaling at least $100 in the past 30 days. Eligibility criteria applies.   \r\n\r\n4.\tMonthly fee waived when you receive a payroll or government benefits direct deposit in the previous monthly statement period. Otherwise, $5 per month.  See our simple fees chart at GO2bank.com/fees\r\n\r\n5.\tSee app for free ATM locations. $3 for out-of-network withdrawals, plus any additional fees the ATM owner or bank may charge. Limits apply.\r\n\r\n6.\tInterest paid quarterly on the average daily balance of savings during the quarter up to a $5,000 balance and if the account is in good standing. Fees on primary deposit account may reduce earnings on your savings account. 4.50% Annual Percentage Yield (APY) as of August 2025. APY may change before or after you open an account.\r\n\r\n7.\tRetail service fee up to $4.95 and limits apply.\r\n\r\n8.\tPreviously authorized transactions and deposits/transfers to your account will function with a locked card.\r\n\r\n9.\tMessage and data rates apply.\r\n\r\n10.\tGreen Dot Bank also operates under the following registered names: GO2bank, GoBank and Bonneville Bank. All other registered trade names are used by, and refer to, a single FDIC-insured bank, Green Dot Bank. Deposits under any of these trade names are deposits with Green Dot Bank and are aggregated for deposit insurance coverage.\r\n\r\nSee Deposit Account Agreement at GO2bank.com/daa for details.\r\n\r\nCards issued by Green Dot Bank, Member FDIC, pursuant to a license from Visa U.S.A., Inc. Visa is a registered trademark of Visa International Service Association.\r\n\r\nTechnology Privacy Statement - www.go2bank.com/techprivacy",
