        "app_name": "Acorns: Save & Invest Money",
        "app_id": "com.acorns.android",
        "category": "Finance",
        "description": "Acorns helps you save, invest, and grow for your future. Our automated saving, investing, and spending tools help you grow your money and financial wellness.\r\n\r\nAt Acorns, we believe that financial wellness and finance education are for everybody. It has nothing to do with how much you make — it’s about finding balance with what you have through better financial decisions. Financial wellness is when you are spending smarter today, saving for tomorrow, and investing for your future all at once.\r\nMore than 14,000,000 Americans have invested over $30,000,000,000 with Acorns. \r\n\r\nAcorns is committed to your security with 2-factor authentication, fraud protection, 256-bit data encryption, and all-digital card lock. Acorns Investment accounts are SIPC-protected up to $500,000, and Acorns checking accounts are FDIC-insured up to $250,000.\r\n\r\nINVEST:\r\n- EASY, AUTOMATED INVESTING\r\nYour money is automatically invested into our expert-built, diversified ETF portfolios. You can Invest Spare Change® each time you make a purchase with the Round-Ups® feature or set up automated recurring investments starting as low as $5.\r\n- INVEST IN BITS OF BITCOIN\r\nRide Bitcoin’s highs and ride out its lows by allocating up to 5% of your diversified portfolio towards a Bitcoin-linked ETF.\r\n- PERSONALIZE YOUR PORTFOLIO\r\nAdd individual stocks and ETFs from the largest 100+ public US companies to your Custom Portfolio.\r\n- INVEST FOR RETIREMENT\r\nSave for retirement with an Acorns Later account and strengthen your future finance plans. Get a 3% IRA match on new contributions during your first year with Acorns Gold.\r\n- INVEST FOR YOUR KIDS\r\nStart building your kids’ futures with Acorns Early Invest, a dedicated investment account for your kids. We’ll match your investments by 1% on up to $7,000 per year — exclusively on Acorns Gold!\r\n\r\nSAVE:\r\n- EMERGENCY SAVINGS\r\nBuild savings for life’s unexpected hiccups, including a 3.35% APY to help your money grow.\r\n- CHECKING\r\nInvest Spare Change® when you spend, and automatically invest a piece of each paycheck to support your daily finance habits with Acorns Checking.\r\n\r\n- MONEY MANAGER\r\nPut your money on autopilot with Money Manager, which smartly splits your money across investing, saving, and spending.\r\n- KIDS & TEEN DEBIT CARD\r\nTeach your kids smart finance habits and financial wellness with an Acorns Early debit card, included in Acorns Gold.\r\n- EARN BONUS INVESTMENTS\r\nShop 10,000+ brands and earn bonus investments and exclusive deals. Plus, earn limited-time referral bonuses of up to $1,200.\r\n- GROW YOUR MONEY KNOWLEDGE\r\nAccess custom articles, videos, courses, and live Q&As to improve your finance knowledge and learn all things money.\r\n\r\nSUBSCRIPTION\r\nWhether you’re new to investing or planning for your family’s future, we bundle our money tools into subscription plans. No hidden costs or transaction fees — just one, transparent monthly payment to start growing your oak.\r\n\r\nBronze ($3/mo)\r\nInvesting tools to get you started on your financial journey\r\nRound-Ups® feature\r\nExpert-built diversified portfolio\r\nRetirement account\r\nChecking account\r\n\r\nSilver ($6/mo)\r\nLevel up your saving and investing skills\r\nEverything in Bronze\r\n1% IRA match on new contributions to your Acorns Later retirement account during your first year with Acorns Silver\r\nEmergency Savings\r\nCourses and videos to help you grow your money knowledge\r\nLive Q&As with investing experts\r\n\r\nGold ($12/mo)\r\nFull suite of saving, investing, and learning tools \r\nEverything in Silver\r\nSmartly split your money across investing, saving and spending with Money Manager\r\n3% IRA match on new contributions to your Acorns Later retirement account during your first year with Acorns Gold\r\nInvestment accounts with a 1% match on up to $7,000 in contributions per year\r\nAcorns Early smart money app and debit card for kids\r\nAbility to add individual stocks and ETFs to your portfolio\r\n$10,000 life insurance policy\r\nFree tax filing, wills & more\r\nSee disclosures above and at www.acorns.com/disclosures\r\n5300 California Ave Irvine CA 92617",
