        "app_name": "Remitly: Transfer money abroad",
        "app_id": "com.remitly.androidapp",
        "category": "Finance",
        "description": "Millions of people trust Remitly globally for fast, secure money transfers and easy mobile payments for international transfers and remittance. Fast, reliable international money transfers\r\n\r\nRemitly offers reliable money transfers and global remittance services with competitive exchange rates and no hidden fees - serving over 175 countries across 100+ currencies. Whether you're making a one-time money transfer or sending regularly, Remitly offers competitive exchange rates, no hidden fees, and every transfer is guaranteed to arrive on time, or your fees are refunded\r\n\r\nRemitly is especially popular for people in the U.S. sending money back home to countries like India, Mexico and the Philippines, helping families stay connected and financially supported across borders.\r\n\r\nMobile payment convenience\r\n\r\nRemitly combines traditional money transfer services with modern mobile payments and delivery to digital wallets. Send money directly to bank accounts, mobile wallets, or choose from approximately 490,000 cash pickup options worldwide. American customers can also complete transfers using a preferred payment method, including bank transfer, debit or credit card, Google Pay or Apple Pay, making it easy to send money overseas anytime. Just note that payment options vary depending on the sender's location.\r\n\r\nTrusted international remittance service\r\n\r\nMillions trust Remitly for safe and secure international remittance and money transfer services. With real-time tracking and notifications, you know where your money is and when it's going to arrive. Remitly is especially popular for customers in the United States who want to send money to India, China, Vietnam, Canada and the Philippines. With quick, secure and reliable overseas transfers, Remitly helps you stay close to family — no matter the distance.\r\n\r\nCross-border business payments made simple\r\n\r\nRemitly also powers international business payments, helping U.S.-based companies send money transfers to contractors, freelancers, and vendors across the world. With transparent pricing and dedicated support, managing global payments is simple and efficient.\r\n\r\nBuilt for freelancers and global earners\r\n\r\nFreelancers can use Remitly’s direct-to-bank, mobile payment and digital wallet tools to:\r\n\r\n- Request payments from clients in the UK, US and Canada.\r\n- Get paid directly into their local bank account or mobile wallet.\r\n- Store funds securely in a Remitly USD wallet*\r\nWithdraw money when exchange rates are favorable\r\n\r\n*Customers can store funds in USD only.\r\n\r\nEasy setup for sending money abroad\r\n\r\nGetting started takes just minutes:\r\n\r\n- Create an account on mobile or desktop\r\n- Enter your destination and transfer amount\r\n- Select your delivery method from options such as bank deposit, mobile wallet, cash pickup or even home delivery.*\r\n- Pay securely and track your international transfer in real time\r\n\r\n*Delivery options vary depending upon the recipient location.\r\n\r\nYou can even send money through WhatsApp, making mobile money transfers even more accessible when you send to Mexico, Colombia, the Dominican Republic, El Salvador, Guatemala, Peru, Nicaragua, Honduras, Ecuador, India, Pakistan, Nepal, Venezuela, and the Philippines. \r\n\r\nWhy choose Remitly for money transfers and remittance?\r\n\r\nRemitly is ideal for:\r\n- Sending money from the U.S. to family in India, the Philippines, and beyond\r\n- Managing international remittances and recurring transfers\r\n- Moving funds between countries securely\r\n- Paying global teams and contractors with money transfers from the US, UK, and Canada\r\n\r\nReferrals must be new Remitly customers and additional send requirements may be required for rewards to apply. Earn rewards for up to 20 successful referrals. Click here for program details (https://www.remitly.com/us/en/home/referral-program-tnc).\r\n\r\nRemitly has offices around the globe. Remitly Global, Inc. is located at 401 Union Street, Suite 1000, Seattle, WA 98101.",
