        "app_name": "Compare rideshares & taxis",
        "app_id": "com.bellhop.app",
        "category": "Travel & Local",
        "description": "Obi – Compare Rideshares & Taxis Instantly\r\n\r\nSave money on every ride you take. Compare Uber, Lyft, Curb, Waymo, and more — all in one app!\r\n\r\nThe award-winning Obi app lets you instantly compare rideshare and taxi prices in real time, helping you find the cheapest ride every time you travel. With Obi, you’ll never overpay again.\r\n\r\n- Compare all major rideshare and taxi apps in seconds\r\n-  Works in 175+ countries — global coverage wherever you go\r\n- Over 1,000,000 users worldwide and growing\r\n- Completely free — no fees, no markups, ever\r\n\r\nHow much can you save?\r\n\r\nSave $20–$50 on airport and longer rides\r\nSave $5–$10 on everyday local trips\r\n\r\nThose savings add up fast — because most drivers drive for multiple platforms, yet each app charges a different price for the same car and driver. Obi shows you the best deal instantly.\r\n\r\nThe only ride price comparison app you need:\r\n\r\nWhether you’re in New York, Los Angeles, London, or Sydney — Obi brings together all leading ride options including Uber, Lyft, Waymo, Bolt, Curb, FreeNow, Cabify, and dozens more.\r\n\r\nSearch, compare, and book — all from one free app.\r\n\r\n🚀 Start saving today\r\n\r\nDownload Obi – Rideshare & Taxi Comparison now and start saving on every trip. Whether it’s your daily commute or an airport ride, Obi helps you ride smarter and spend less.\r\n\r\nrideobi.com",
