        "description": "GO South Placer is on-demand transit in the palm of your hand. Book a ride throughout Placer County Transit and Roseville Transit service areas (Roseville Transit Arrow). Reservations can be made same day or in advance – just tap and ride! Fares can be purchased through the app or with cash on-board the vehicle.",
