        "app_name": "Curb One - for Taxi Drivers",
        "app_id": "com.curb.one",
        "category": "Travel & Local",
        "description": "Download Curb One, the all-in-one app for licensed taxi drivers. \r\n\r\nSeparate from the Curb Driver app, Curb One is the only taxi driver app featuring an integrated meter, payments, and third-party trip offers in one solution. With smart navigation and seamless operations, it has everything drivers need to maximize earning potential with every shift.\r\n\r\nKey Features:\r\n* No Hardware, No Hassle: Eliminate separate devices and installation headaches with everything integrated into your phone.\r\n* Easy, Fast Trip Payments: With Tap to Pay on iPhone, accept contactless payments right from your phone—no external terminal needed.\r\nIntegrated Taxi Meter: Digital meter with built-in GPS and tariff regulations ensures accurate, compliant fare calculation every trip.\r\n* Low-Competitive Settlement & Processing Rates: Keep more of what you earn with low processing fees on every transaction.\r\n* More Trips, More Earnings: The only marketplace built to bring you more trips from trusted demand partners, maximizing your earning potential.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions, please feel free to email driver_support@gocurb.com.\r\n\r\nFor drivers, continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.\r\n\r\nBy downloading the app, you agree to receive communications from Curb, including push notifications; and (ii) to allow Curb to collect your device's language settings. You can opt out of receiving push notifications through your device settings.",
