        "description": "Get a public transit ride whenever you need it! \r\n\r\nRides on Demand helps you find and share rides with people going in the same direction directly from your phone. It’s cheaper than driving yourself or taking a cab and better for the environment too!\r\n\r\nJust tap, book and ride away!\r\n\r\nWe help make public transit inclusive, equitable and easily accessible to ALL types of riders, regardless of age, eligibility or special requirements and our latest update exemplifies that commitment.\r\n\r\nOur Latest Update - Helping eligibility-based riders book trips easily\r\n\r\nInstant Eligibility-Based Rides*: \r\nADA, Veterans, Specialized Transit or Senior Service riders can now book spontaneous trips through Rides on Demand, without days of advance notice!\r\n\r\nReal-Time Eligibility Status*: \r\nCheck your eligibility status, book space for escorts or companions, service animals and more on the go.\r\n\r\nNo More Waiting on the Phone: \r\nDon’t bother waiting on hold and book your trips with a few taps instead - directly from your phone! \r\n\r\nDetailed Ride History*:\r\nView ride history for trips booked via the app or Passenger Portal \r\nUser Interface Enhancements:\r\n\r\nSee your trip options and book them faster!\r\n\r\n*Availability may vary by city or region",
