    {
        "app_name": "Freenow by Lyft - taxi & more",
        "app_id": "taxi.android.client",
        "category": "Travel & Local",
        "description": "At Freenow, we believe every journey should be seamless and trustworthy. That's why we're focusing more than ever on getting you reliable taxis, whenever and wherever you need them. Connect to opportunities, loved ones and new experiences with peace of mind. \r\n\r\nWherever life takes you, Freenow is your steadfast partner across 9 European countries. \r\n\r\nWHAT YOU CAN DO WITH FREENOW:\r\nGet a taxi you can trust: your journey starts with a tap, connecting you to professional, dependable drivers in well-maintained vehicles. \r\nFlexible travel options: explore city life with our eScooters, eBikes, eMopeds, Carsharing, or private hire vehicles (Ride). \r\nPublic transport tickets: buy tickets for transit directly in the app (where available).\r\nCar Rental: need a car for longer? Rent one through the app.\r\n\r\nEFFORTLESS PAYMENTS:\r\nForget the hassle of cash. Pay securely in seconds using your preferred method: card, Google Pay, Apple Pay or PayPal. Plus, keep an eye out for discounts and vouchers!\r\n\r\nSMOOTH AIRPORT TRANSFERS:\r\nWhether it’s an early flight or a late arrival, count on Freenow for reliable 24/7 airport transfers. We cover major European airports, including London (Heathrow, City, Gatwick, Stansted), Dublin, Frankfurt, Madrid-Barajas, Barcelona El-Prat, Munich, Rome Fiumicino, Athens, Warsaw, Manchester, Düsseldorf, Vienna Schwechat, Milan Malpensa, Berlin and Malaga. \r\n\r\nJOURNEYS MADE EASY:\r\nPlan ahead: prebook your taxi up to 90 days in advance.\r\nSeamless pickups: use our in-app chat to connect with your driver.\r\nStay connected: share your trip location with friends and family for peace of mind.\r\nPersonalise your experience: rate drivers and save your favourite addresses for even faster bookings.\r\n\r\nTRAVEL FOR WORK? FREENOW FOR BUSINESS:\r\nSimplify your business trips and expense reporting. Your employer might even offer a monthly Mobility Benefits Card for your travel. Talk to your company about us.\r\n\r\nSPREAD THE FREENOW FEELING:\r\nInvite your friends and they’ll get a voucher for their first ride. Once they’ve completed it, a voucher will land in your account too. Check the app for details.\r\n\r\nDownload Freenow today and get travel you can trust.\r\n\r\nFreenow is now part of Lyft, a leader in transport. This exciting collaboration combines Freenow's trusted presence in Europe with Lyft's commitment to delivering reliable, safe and people-focused journeys. With this partnership, we're building a global network to provide you with seamless travel options and exceptional service, whether you're at home or abroad.",
