        "app_name": "Vay - rent a car nearby",
        "app_id": "io.vay.rider",
        "category": "Travel & Local",
        "description": "Vay delivers affordable, on-demand electric cars straight to your doorstep.\r\nUp to 50% cheaper than Uber, Lyft, or a traditional taxi, when you pick up and park the car yourself.\r\n\r\nWelcome to Vay — the smarter way to rent cars, request rides, and experience the future of car sharing in the city.\r\n\r\nRent Driverless Cars, Delivered to You:\r\n\r\nWith Vay, you don’t walk to a lot or stand at a national car rental counter. You open the Vay car rental app, request a car nearby, and your vehicle is delivered driverlessly within minutes.\r\n\r\nThink robotaxi convenience — but you drive the car yourself.\r\n\r\nWhether it’s everyday travel, a quick trip, or business trips across the Strip or Downtown, Vay makes city car rental effortless.\r\nCurrently available in Las Vegas, and expanding to more cities soon. Stay tuned as Vay brings driverless electric car rentals to new locations!\r\n\r\nA New Kind of Car Sharing Rental that combines\r\n-The freedom of rental cars\r\n-The ease of a taxi\r\n-The flexibility of a car-sharing app\r\n\r\nYour car is delivered driverlessly.\r\nYou drive wherever you need to go.\r\nEnd your rental easily in approved parking zones — or let the Remote Valet handle parking.\r\nIt's a rental car delivered, reimagined.\r\n\r\nWhy Choose Vay?\r\n\r\n-Cars Delivered Driverlessly: No rental counter. No waiting. Rent cars and get it delivered directly to you.\r\n-Fully Electric Rentals: Clean, quiet city cars for easy driving.\r\n-Cheap Car Rentals Without Hidden Fees: Save up to 50% compared to taxi services and rideshare, when you pick up and park the car yourself.\r\n-Flexible Hourly Car Rentals: Perfect for city trips, errands, or nearby car rental needs.\r\n-Simple Car Ordering: Request a car in seconds and get moving fast.\r\n\r\nPerfect For\r\n-Everyday travel\r\n-City trip adventures\r\n-Business trips\r\n-Quick trip & errands\r\n-Replacing taxi rides\r\n-Exploring nearby destinations\r\n\r\nVay takes car sharing further than other car rental marketplaces: Vay cars arrive driverlessly.\r\n\r\nDownload Vay today and experience the magic of driverless delivery, electric rentals, and smart urban mobility.\r\n\r\nQuestions? support@vay.io\r\n\r\nHelp center: vay.io/help",
