    {
        "app_name": "Quick Ride- Cab Taxi & Carpool",
        "app_id": "com.disha.quickride",
        "category": "Travel & Local",
        "description": "Quick Ride is one of India’s largest Cab Taxi & Carpool App.\r\n\r\nOne App with Dual Advantage:\r\n1. Taxi Cab Booking App in India : Outstation Taxi, Airport Taxi, Local Taxi, Taxi Rentals, Cab Rentals at best fares.\r\n2. Carpool & Bikepool\r\n\r\nWe operate all over India, with significant presence in Delhi-NCR, Mumbai, Bangalore, Pune, Kolkata, Chennai, Hyderabad, Kochi and Trivandrum.\r\nWe have Cabs in Hyderabad, Cabs in Bengaluru, Cabs in Delhi, Cabs in Mumbai, Cabs in Chennai, Cabs in Pune.\r\nQuick Ride can help you for daily office travel, scheduled trips, airport transfers, and your outstation trips with lower fares. Quick Ride provides you a taxi service with \"\"Best Taxi, Best Fare\"\".\r\n\r\nSafe Ride Cab service from Quick Ride!\r\nYou can book taxi for your daily commute, Airport travel or for outstation trips. You can book instant or schedule in advance. You can hire from our wide fleet of sedan, hatchback and SUV cars.\r\n\r\nOur popular travel options are -\r\n1. Airport Taxi Booking, Airport Cab - For critical airport travel, schedule in advance and get the taxi on-time with 10% cheaper fares.\r\n2. Local City Taxi - Going to office, party or shopping, Hail a ride locally with a hygienic taxi at lower fares.\r\n3. Rental - Use it for as low as 2 hrs / 20 kms and upto 12 hrs / 120 kms. Good Cabs with Short Trips or Long trips with multiple stops.\r\n4. Outstation - For car booking for outstation or outstation car rental, it can be within state or interstate, get better quality taxi at assured 5% lower fares than others with transparent billing. You can also do a one way drop taxi.\r\n\r\nCarpooling and Bike Pooling:\r\nIf you have a vehicle (car / bike) and driving alone, Quick Ride will help you to connect with other like-minded professionals who are traveling on the same route – same time. You can share empty seats with others by Offering Ride and share fuel costs. You can save upto Rs.15k per month, help reduce traffic congestion and enhance your network. Your Route. Your Time. Your Choice of members.\r\nIf you are looking for a travel option, You can find a ride to share for a safe , economical & comfortable commute option via carpooling or bikepooling. With Quick Ride, you can save 80% of your travel costs (Carpool ride cost is at 1/5th of the Taxi cost). Carpooling is safe, as the profiles are verified and you can reduce travel time. Networking on the go is bonus. Ride fares start as low as Rs. 4/km\r\n\r\nKey features of Overall Quick Ride App:\r\n- Enterprise security features\r\n- Real time - route matches\r\n- Instant ride confirmations\r\n- Live tracking with ETA\r\n- Carpool groups for the same community/tech park/company\r\n- Group chat with co-riders to coordinate pickup\r\n- Ride Givers can set their own Fare\r\n- Cashless payment system with multiple payment & Redemption options.\r\n- Instant redemptions\r\n- Recurring ride facility\r\n\r\nIntercity Carpool\r\nWorried about Costly Taxi fare or surge in Bus fares during holidays?\r\nTry carpool for your outstation travels. It is Safe & Comfortable. Popular carpool routes are Bengaluru – Mysuru, Bengaluru – Chennai, Mumbai – Pune, Delhi – Agra, Hyderabad – Vijayawada, Kochi – Trivandrum, Delhi – Chandigarh\r\n\r\nKey Benefits of Quick Ride Taxi:\r\n- Consistent and Lower fares (No Abnormal Surge fares )\r\n- Pre Booking option\r\n- Friendly Driver Support\r\n- When you take Taxi from Quick Ride, the driver will get 50% higher net take home as we take less commission. This makes drivers Happy and Loyal to You.\r\n\r\nRegister now to get your first ride FREE / Free reward points for Carpooling.\r\nFor Taxi, Use Promo code - FIRSTTAXI & Get Rs 50 off.",
