    {
        "app_name": "Bharat Taxi - Cab, Auto & Bike",
        "app_id": "in.mobility.bharatTaxi",
        "category": "Travel & Local",
        "description": "Bharat Taxi is India’s first cooperative ride-hailing app, built for riders and owned by drivers. Book Auto, Bike, and Cab rides with transparent pricing, faster pickups, and industry-leading safety features. Backed by a driver cooperative model supported by the Ministry of Cooperation.\r\n\r\nWhether it’s your daily office commute, a late-night ride, or a quick city trip- Bharat Taxi gets you there safely and affordably.\r\n\r\n🚨 Your Safety Comes First\r\n\r\nBharat Taxi is designed with built-in safety features to ensure peace of mind on every ride:\r\n\r\n🛡️ One-tap SOS button – instantly connects to local police control rooms\r\n📞 Emergency contact alerts – your trusted contacts are notified immediately\r\n🚨 Siren button – trigger a loud in-app siren during emergencies\r\n📍 Live ride tracking – share your trip in real time with friends & family. Ride with confidence- day or night.\r\n\r\n🚕 Why Choose Bharat Taxi?\r\n\r\n💯 Zero commission rides – fair fares for customers, full earnings for drivers\r\n⚡ Fast bookings – get the nearest driver in seconds\r\n💸 Transparent fares – clear pricing with no hidden charges\r\n😊 Lower cancellations – happier drivers, more reliable rides\r\n💸 Easy payments – pay via UPI or cash\r\n\r\n🚖 Ride Options Available\r\n\r\n• Bharat Auto – Short, quick city rides\r\n• Bharat Bike – Fast and budget-friendly travel\r\n• Cab Economy – Affordable daily rides\r\n• Cab Priority – Faster pickups when you’re in a hurry\r\n• Sedan – Comfortable rides with more space\r\n• XL – Spacious cars for families or luggage\r\n\r\n🌱 Built on a Cooperative Model\r\n\r\nUnlike traditional ride-hailing apps, Bharat Taxi operates on a cooperative mobility model- where drivers are partners, not contractors. This means better service, ethical pricing, and a more sustainable transport ecosystem for India.\r\n\r\n📲 Download Bharat Taxi – India’s 1st Cooperative Taxi App\r\nInstall. Set location. Book your safe ride.\r\n\r\n🔗 Stay Connected\r\nInstagram: @bharattaxiofficial\r\nTwitter (X): @coopbharattaxi",
        "permissions": {
