        "app_name": "GoRide: Cab, Bike Taxi & Pool",
        "app_id": "com.shi.goride_customer",
        "category": "Travel & Local",
        "description": "Go Ride makes intercity travel simple. Book cabs, SUVs, and more for one-way or round trips with transparent pricing and a smooth booking experience.\r\n\r\nWHY GO RIDE\r\n• Intercity travel: Plan one-way or round trips between cities with ease.\r\n• Choice of vehicles: Select from cabs, SUVs, and other options to match your trip and group size.\r\n• Transparent pricing: See fare estimates before you book. No hidden charges.\r\n• Secure payments: Pay online via UPI, cards, or wallets through a secure payment gateway.\r\n• Verified drivers: Connect with drivers for a safer, more reliable journey.\r\n\r\nHOW IT WORKS\r\n1. Enter pickup and destination.\r\n2. Pick your vehicle type and travel date/time.\r\n3. Get your fare and confirm your booking.\r\n4. Choose your driver, track your ride, and pay securely when you’re done.\r\n\r\nFEATURES\r\n• One-way and round-trip booking\r\n• Multiple vehicle types (cab, SUV, etc.)\r\n• Fare estimate before booking\r\n• Secure online payment (UPI, cards, wallets)\r\n• Driver rating and feedback\r\n• Booking history and trip details\r\n• Notifications for booking and ride updates\r\n• Help centre: FAQ, Terms, and Privacy Policy\r\n• Support via phone and email\r\n\r\nWhether you’re travelling for work or leisure, Go Ride helps you book intercity cabs and SUVs quickly and pay securely. Download Go Ride and plan your next trip.",
