    {
        "app_name": "Grab - Taxi & Food Delivery",
        "app_id": "com.grabtaxi.passenger",
        "category": "Travel & Local",
        "description": "Grab is #1 all-in-one taxi, ride hailing, transport, express grocery shopping and food delivery app in Southeast Asia \r\n\r\n🏃In a rush? We’ll get you where you’re going in style. Find a taxi, carpool, or hire a car! \r\n🍔 Satisfy your cravings: order food delivery from your favourite restaurants \r\n🛍️ Had a long day? Save yourself a trip to the store with grocery delivery \r\n💸 No wallet needed: use Grab to pay for shopping across the city \r\n\r\nAll in one simple, convenient app. Whatever you need, from food delivery to a last-minute taxi, Grab has you covered. \r\n\r\n🚕 Taxi, cab, and transport services for any budget (and occasion!) ⭐️ \r\n\r\nRide taxis in comfort: Get affordable, upfront fixed rates with JustGrab or GrabTaxi – wherever you’re going.\r\n\r\nDiscover seamless city travel in the ultimate taxi app for booking a safe and convenient ride whenever you need it. Wherever your heading, Grab makes it easy to get a reliable taxi ride in minutes. Our numerous safety features protect both you and drivers.\r\n\r\nEnjoy the flexibility of modern transport by choosing from a range of taxi options, including fast rideshare solutions. Every taxi ride is designed for comfort, efficiency, and peace of mind. Communicate with the drivers seamlessly with Grab’s built-in translation feature.\r\n\r\nCarpool like a pro thanks to GrabHitch, with advance bookings and cashless payments… or rideshare in style with a GrabExec limousine ride!\r\n\r\nNeed extra assistance? Find a more accessible taxi ride with GrabAssist and get picked up by Agency for Integrated Care (AIC) taxi drivers. \r\n\r\nWant to be in the driving seat? Hire an affordable luxury car through GrabCar, GrabCar Plus or GrabCar Premium. Ride solo or with your crew. \r\n\r\nTravel with friends, family, or even ride with pets! 🐶 Book taxis with bicycle racks, space for furry friends and booster seats for little ones – or minibuses for larger parties. Try GrabCar for Cyclists, GrabPet, GrabFamily or GrabCoach. \r\n\r\n\r\n🍕 Food delivery to suit every taste 🍟 \r\n\r\nGet food delivery from your favourite restaurant or mart, delivered straight to your doorstep, with GrabFood. \r\n\r\nUsing a food delivery app can save you time, offering a variety of cuisines at your fingertips.\r\n\r\nOrder groceries, healthcare and beauty products, gifts, and more with GrabMart. Put your feet up, and get delivery services within 30 minutes! \r\n\r\nSafely send your items anywhere – book affordable, reliable, insured couriers with GrabExpress. \r\n\r\nForgotten a birthday? Save the day with a digital gift card! Give money off Grab taxi rides, food delivery, or groceries, thanks to GrabGift.   \r\n\r\n\r\n💸 Designed for seamless shopping 🛍️ \r\n\r\nSwitch to secure, cashless payments for taxi rides, transport services, food delivery, grocery orders and more with GrabPay. Transaction history is easy to view in-app. \r\n\r\nTake out flexible insurance to suit you with GrabInsure. Find a plan that suits you, and sort everything through the Grab app. \r\n\r\nNeed more time? Pay for Grab delivery orders and online shopping at the end of the month, in one single payment, with PayLater by Grab. \r\n\r\nDon’t want to carry your wallet? Set up a pre-paid GrabPay Card and shop at any physical or online shop!   \r\n\r\n\r\n🎁 Earn rewards for using Grab ✨ \r\n\r\nOrder the things you love with Grab, and get points to redeem on awesome deals with GrabRewards. It’s that simple! \r\n\r\n\r\nDid you know? \r\n\r\nYou can use the Grab app in 8 countries: Singapore, Indonesia, Malaysia, Thailand, Vietnam, Philippines, Cambodia and Myanmar. \r\n\r\nFind out more about us at https://www.grab.com/  \r\nFollow us on Facebook (https://www.fb.com/grab), X (https://X.com/grabsg) and Instagram (https://www.instagram.com/grab_sg) \r\n\r\nPrivacy policy at https://www.grab.com/privacy \r\nTerms of Service: https://grab.com/terms \r\nOSS attributions: http://grb.to/oss-attributions",
